languages.text: "Пролить кровь этих поверженных слабаков, всего-то? Я с радостью принесу эту пустяковую жертву! Признаться, я ожидал{mf||а} большего от Ангелов Императора".
"Spill the blood of these defeated weaklings? Just that and nothing else? I will gladly make that trifling sacrifice! I must admit I expected more from the Emperor's Angels."

languages.text: “让这些不值一提的弱者血流成河？仅此而已吗？我很愿意献上这些微不足道的祭品！我得承认，我原以为帝皇的天使没这么无能。”
languages.original_text: "Spill the blood of these defeated weaklings? Just that and nothing else? I will gladly make that trifling sacrifice! I must admit I expected more from the Emperor's Angels."

languages.text: "Das Blut dieser besiegten Schwächlinge vergießen? Nur das, sonst nichts? Dieses lächerliche Opfer erbringe ich doch gerne! Ich muss gestehen, dass ich von den Engeln des Imperators mehr erwartet hätte."
languages.original_text: "Spill the blood of these defeated weaklings? Just that and nothing else? I will gladly make that trifling sacrifice! I must admit I expected more from the Emperor's Angels."

languages.text: «¿Derramar la sangre de estos alfeñiques derrotados? ¿Eso y nada más? ¡Ofreceré {mf|encantado|encantada} ese mísero sacrificio! Debo admitir que esperaba más de los Ángeles del Emperador».
languages.original_text: "Spill the blood of these defeated weaklings? Just that and nothing else? I will gladly make that trifling sacrifice! I must admit I expected more from the Emperor's Angels."

languages.text: « Verser le sang de ces misérables avortons, rien de plus ? C'est un sacrifice insignifiant auquel je consentirai avec plaisir ! Je dois admettre que je m'attendais à mieux de la part des anges de l'Empereur. »
languages.original_text: "Spill the blood of these defeated weaklings? Just that and nothing else? I will gladly make that trifling sacrifice! I must admit I expected more from the Emperor's Angels."

languages.text: 「敗れた弱者の血を流す？ただそれだけか？私は喜んでその些細な犠牲を払う！実のところ皇帝の天使からはそれ以上のものを予想していたのだが…」
languages.original_text: "Spill the blood of these defeated weaklings? Just that and nothing else? I will gladly make that trifling sacrifice! I must admit I expected more from the Emperor's Angels."

languages.text: "Zaten yenilmiş olan iradesi zayıfların kanını mı dökmemi istiyorsun? Bu kadar mı? Bu değersiz fedakârlığı yapmaya hazırım! Dürüst olacağım, İmparator'un Melekleri'nden daha fazlasını beklerdim."
